int parseint(string x)
{
	int res = 0;
	int sz = x.size();
	for(int i = 0; i < sz; ++i)
		if(x[i] >= '0' && x[i] <= '9')res = 10 * res + x[i] - '0';
	if(x[0] == '-')return (-1*res);
	return res;
}
